headline.main: Lions Run Amok in Try-Fest Against Waratahs
headline.print_headline: Lions Run Amok in Try-Fest Against Waratahs

lead_paragraph: The Lions ran in eight tries and claimed a bonus point as they beat the New South Wales Waratahs 55-36 in a free-flowing Super Rugby clash at Ellis Park on Saturday.
